com.calendarfx.view

Class RequestEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.EventObject
      • javafx.event.Event
        • com.calendarfx.view.RequestEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable

    public final class RequestEvent
extends Event
    A specialized event class used by date controls to request that the UI shows a given date, dateTime, month, or year. This event gets, for example, fired when the user double clicks on a day in the YearPage of the CalendarView. The CalendarView will then automatically switch to the DayPage.
    See Also:
